data.description: Price Reduced on this perfect starter home or could be a great investment property. This home offers a spacious living room, ceiling fan adjoined to the dining area. Kitchen has laminate flooring, gas stove and refrigerator. There are two bedrooms and a full bath with laminate floors, cabinet/sink and mirror. The third room could be used as an office/bonus room. Large backyard and the front yard is fully fenced and has a great covered porch. Don't miss out, schedule a showing today.
